* Seller is giving $10,000 to buyer, use as buyer chooses!
* Seller is also providing a 1 year home warranty for the buyer
HVAC replaced in 2023!
New dehumidifier was added to the crawlspace in 2023!

Discover unbeatable value with this single-family ranch floor plan home! Boasting 4 bedrooms plus a study, 2 full bathrooms, and a massive flat yard, this property is a true gem. The interior features granite counters with a bar, stainless steel appliances, a stylish tile backsplash, and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. The spacious half-acre lot provides ample outdoor space for various activities. 
 Centrally located to Fayetteville, Raleigh, and Wilmington, this home provides convenient access to multiple areas, making it an ideal hub for a variety of lifestyles. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a home that combines comfort, style, and unbeatable value.
